item.title: Initial Commit
item.description: So here I am, once more, trying to have some sort of blog or journal. I’ll try to write about interesting pieces of code that I’ve written, problems I had to solve, books I’ve read (or dropped), et cetera. Don’t get your hopes too high, though, I’m lazy and tend to forget doing this kind of stuff.
